You play the game your way, and I'll play it mine, but to basically say teh 'I don't want to be hit less because it lowers my DPS from damage shields' really smacks of a 'everyone who doesn't play like I do is stupid' attitude and is in fact a very small and narrowminded wiew (imo). <p><center><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=30466" TARGET="_blank"><image src = "http://www.catplex.org/chilau/chilau_fk5.jpg"></a>
